706338f-a.text:
1. Prospect Avenue, north side, west from Fifth Avenue--from underneath the B. M. T. "El." Note the enclosed exterior stairway leading up to the second floor of the corner house.
June 14, 1940
P. L. Sperr

2. Prospect Ave., n.w. corner, at 5th Ave., B'klyn.
Nov. 5, 1941
P.L. Sperr, photographer

3. Prospect Ave. adjoining n.e. corner of 5th Ave., B'klyn.
Nov. 16, 1941
P.L. Sperr, photographer
